      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:7:5",
      "text": [
        " حَدُّ الرَّجْمِ فِي الزِّنَى أَنْ يَشْهَدَ أَرْبَعَةٌ أَنَّهُمْ رَأَوْهُ يُدْخِلُ وَ يُخْرِجُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Muhammad Bin Al Hassan Al Basry, from Hammad Bin Isa, from Shuayb Al Aqarquqy, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the stoning regarding the adultery is that four should testify that they had seen him enter and exit’."
        ]
      }
